  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Groupware系统的架构图，核心是展示用户请求如何从聊天室入口经过DNS、CDN最终到达存储层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，入口是Groupware_ChatRoom对吗？那DNS层我打算用一个子图来包裹，里面放Route 53组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "R53"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但R53节点本身也叫Groupware_ChatRoom，这是为了体现DNS解析后还是回到聊天室域名的概念。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "DNS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，DNS子图已经画好，用了浅黄色背景。现在我来添加CDN层，这个子图需要包含Edge节点、Lambda、证书和缓存四个组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CDN层用粉色系吧，比较醒目。对了，Edge节点叫Groupware_ChatRoom，Lambda叫Groupware_KanbanBoard，证书是WikiPage，缓存是IssueTracker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "CDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "CDN子图画好了。接下来是存储层，我打算用绿色系，包含OAI和FILES两个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STORAGE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "存储层的子图名称是Groupware_WikiPage，OAI节点叫Groupware_KanbanBoard，FILES叫Groupware_IssueTracker。注意OAI是Origin Access Identity的意思。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STORAGE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "存储层也完成了。现在开始画连接线。用户到R53走HTTPS，这条线需要标注一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，USER到R53标注\"HTTPS\"。然后R53指向EDGE，EDGE到LAMBDA，LAMBDA到CERT，CERT到CACHE，这些都不需要额外标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "前面的连线都画好了。现在CACHE到OAI，以及OAI到FILES的连线需要处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "CACHE到OAI这条线要标注\"OAI Only\"，表示只有OAI能访问缓存回源，然后OAI再到FILES获取实际文件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有连线和标注都完成了。现在给各个子图和入口节点加上样式，USER用蓝色系，DNS黄色，CDN粉色，STORAGE绿色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "样式看起来不错。不过我想确认一下，整个流程是：用户从ChatRoom出发，经过KanbanBoard形式的DNS解析，进入SprintBacklog形式的CDN层处理，最后落到WikiPage形式的存储层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，虽然节点名称都复用了Groupware的模块名，但结构上是标准的云架构：DNS解析→边缘节点→函数计算→证书验证→缓存→身份验证→文件存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有个细节，R53到EDGE的箭头方向对吗？应该是DNS解析完成后指向CDN边缘节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认过了，R53指向EDGE，方向正确。需要我调整什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不用调整，方向是对的。我再检查一下CACHE到OAI的标注——\"OAI Only\"这个说明很重要，强调安全性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CACHE",
        "OAI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "标注已确认。整个图现在26个元素左右，结构清晰。需要我补充任何说明文字吗？",
      "elements_involved": [],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "暂时不需要额外文字。不过我想再确认一下各个Groupware模块的对应关系：ChatRoom作为入口和DNS解析点，KanbanBoard同时出现在DNS和Lambda，WikiPage作为存储层外壳和证书节点，IssueTracker作为缓存和文件节点——这样设计是有意为之吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "STORAGE",
        "CACHE",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是的，这是为了体现Groupware各模块在云架构中的多重角色。比如KanbanBoard既负责调度（DNS层面的解析调度）又负责计算（Lambda函数处理），IssueTracker既做热点数据缓存又做冷数据文件存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LAMBDA",
        "CACHE",
        "FILES",
        "R53"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了这个设计意图。那SprintBacklog作为CDN层的外壳也很合理，代表内容的迭代分发。最后检查一下颜色对比度，确保投影演示时能看清。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经优化了颜色对比度，蓝色#1565c0、黄色#f9a825、粉色#c2185b、绿色#2e7d32，都是高对比度的深色边框配浅色填充。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "很好。等等，我突然想到——OAI节点的名称是Groupware_KanbanBoard，但之前Lambda也是KanbanBoard，这样会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OAI",
        "LAMBDA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "确实，两个节点名称相同但功能不同。不过根据需求，OAI和LAMBDA都命名为Groupware_KanbanBoard是有意体现KanbanBoard模块的双重职责：计算处理和身份验证。如果容易混淆，我可以备注说明。",
      "elements_involved": [
